(4) inharitance:
~> ine class dirived properties of another class its called inharitance
~> A class which is inherited by B class
~> there are IS-A relationship between multiple classes
        class A     (super class) (base class)      (parent class)
              |
              V
        class B     (sub class)   (dirived class)    (child class)
~> there are 5 types of inharitance
:1:> single level inharitance
:2:> multi level inharitance
:3:> multiple inharitance
:4:> hierarchical inharitance
:5:> hybrid inharitance

---------
(1) single level inharitance:
~> one parent class and one child class

            class A (parent)
                  |
                  V
            class B (child)

---------
(2) multi level inharitance:
~> on parent class ans child class and childs child class
                    class A (parent)
                          |
                          V
                    class B (child)
                          |
                          V
                    class C (childs child)
---------
(3) multiple inharitance:
~> multiple parent class and one child class
                class A     class B     class C
                    |           |           |
                    -------------------------
                                |
                                V
                          class D
----------
(4) hierarchical inharitance:
~> hierarchilcal inharitance one parent class and multiple chile class
                            class A
                               |
            -------------------------------------
            |           |            |           |
class       B           C            D           E  
------------
(5) hybrid inharitance:
~> hybrid inharitance is a cobination of single level,multiple and hierarchical inharitance
            A
            |
    ---------------------
    |                   |
    B                   C
    ---------------------
            |
            D

            or

            A               B
            |               |
            C               D
            -----------------
                    |
                    E    
